\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You are lucky if you have the luxury of space in your home. You can install this customised black and white corner wardrobe with shelves in your bedroom or add this as an extension to your bedroom. It is a creative mix of open-style and close-style design elements. It also has designated spaces for each clothing item to help you put together your perfect look for the day while also having easy access. The open lofts are an added benefit to store your seasonal clothes too.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21010440\/customised-wardrobe-door-shelves.jpg\" alt=\"Customised wardrobe door design with black and white corner wardrobe with shelves in your bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-6159\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21010440\/customised-wardrobe-door-shelves.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21010440\/customised-wardrobe-door-shelves-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21010440\/customised-wardrobe-door-shelves-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21010440\/customised-wardrobe-door-shelves-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Designer Wardrobe Doors<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you like experimenting and making unconventional choices, then you can try this <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/designer-wardrobe-ideas\/\">designer wardrobe<\/a>. Its unique door design and diagonal placement of handles is appealing and can serve as great conversation-starters. This wardrobe looks contemporary and comes with an attached bookshelf and study table to make it more multi-functional in nature.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure